item.title: Team .EXE (joining the Team - part 1)
item.author: rishabh0402+website@gmail.com (Rishabh)
item.description: Its raining outside & i am writing this post , Hope it helps :-) It was my 2nd year & SFD’s work was in progress & for that I’d been assigned a senior to work with & he was Arun Chaudhary (core coordinator of Team EXE) & believe me he was impressed with my work (what say Arun Sir? ;-) ) & he’d suggested me to join the team during nimbus(Tech fest of NIT Hamirpur) 2k16.
